## Important Notes
- `RRPartOwner` StringValue must exist inside part before any Sync* calls work
- `SyncAPI:Invoke` only works when Building Tools is **equipped** (in workspace)
- `EscalateEvent:FireServer(PartOwnership, {part})` — first arg is the MODULE not the player!
  The server reads the calling player from the remote event automatically
- `UnionColoring` not `UnionColor` for SyncColor
- `SyncResize` takes both Size AND CFrame — use this instead of SyncSize + SyncMove separately
- Direct property setting (`part.Color = x`) only shows client-side, does NOT replicate
- Metamethod hooking = instant kick ("namecallInstance detector detected")

